{"metadata":{"title":"getUserId","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"getUserId"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)getUserId","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getUserId","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"Retrieves the current user identifier.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/getUserId"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/getuserid"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"getUserId","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The current user identifier (custom user ID or HWID)"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Returns the user ID that was previously set via ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setUserId:"},{"text":", or the HWID if no custom","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user ID has been set."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sync user ID with analytics platforms:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class AnalyticsCoordinator {","","    func syncIdentifiers() {","        let userId = Pushwoosh.configure.getUserId()","        let hwid = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","","        \/\/ Sync with various analytics platforms","        Analytics.identify(userId)","        Crashlytics.setUserID(userId)","        MixpanelInstance.identify(distinctId: userId)","","        \/\/ Log device mapping for debugging","        Logger.debug(\"User identity: userId=\\(userId), hwid=\\(hwid)\")","    }","","    func trackEventWithUserContext(_ event: String, properties: [String: Any]) {","        var enrichedProperties = properties","        enrichedProperties[\"pushwoosh_user_id\"] = Pushwoosh.configure.getUserId()","        enrichedProperties[\"pushwoosh_hwid\"] = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","","        Analytics.track(event, properties: enrichedProperties)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","type":"topic","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/getUserId":{"title":"getUserId","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/getuserid","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getUserId"}],"nav